{"tid":1716784,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有d唔算好關抗爭既事想分享","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:08:41.000Z","uid":63670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ac858b5dd11e51b63f0a422b43f454a51e5564","tid":1716784,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:26:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟最近聽聞左大陸既拘留所既用刑<br />\n(朋友親戚入過去)<br />\n大概就係：<br />\n首先大家都知大陸可以拘留嫌疑犯超過48h<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係入面呢如果有唔聽話既嫌疑犯呢<br />\n佢哋會上腳鐐先啦<br />\n如果無打招呼,無家人寄錢既話,唔聽話<br />\n就先將你兩隻手分別吊起(手扣)<br />\n｜＼o／｜<br />\n｜     |    ｜<br />\n｜   /  \\   ｜<br />\n<br />\n大概如上<br />\n然後濕d大毛巾,一條一條放上你膊頭度<br />\n放到你叫痛為止,再加幾條,一個鐘後再探你<br />\n(有d殺人嫌疑犯好硬頸唔會叫,放到d公安驚就會放翻落黎,所以企硬真係好重要)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至於點解分享呢,我自己都唔知<br />\n或者唔想香港變成咁掛<br />\n留意返,純粹只係嫌疑犯都咁樣對待<br />\n真係地獄黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我frd親戚係入面度過左一年都未判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c69912ac32b0072f3cff1e40a73ca9c13a22d1","tid":1716784,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"今日見到話有香港抗爭者入大陸d拘留所<br />\n入黎推翻<br />\n大家要記得仲有好多自己人係度<br />\n受不人道對待<br />\n甚至可能出唔返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496a5c89ccd12b93b8bfba0de8d00be2c9dddca6","tid":1716784,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dc4c458c74e8d889695b0e7103e47b54820b87","tid":1716784,"uid":306684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif